# System Documentation: Multi-business SaaS Inventory Management System

## 1. Executive Summary
This project is a high-end, premium-designed Multi-business SaaS Inventory Management System tailored for the Bangladeshi retail market. It features a category-aware dynamic architecture that adapts to different business types (Fashion, Electronics, Grocery, etc.), multi-branch support, comprehensive accounting, and a multi-payment POS system.

## 2. Global Architecture
The system is built as a highly responsive single-page experience (SPA-like) using:
- **Core**: Semantic HTML5, Vanilla JavaScript.
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with a custom design system ([js/tailwind-config.js](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/js/tailwind-config.js) and [css/style.css](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/css/style.css)).
- **State Management**: Localized state container ([js/state.js](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/js/state.js)) using `localStorage` for cross-page persistence.
- **Layout**: Dynamic layout injector ([js/layout.js](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/js/layout.js)) that handles the global Sidebar, Navbar, and notifications.

### Dynamic Category Logic
The system uses a unique `CATEGORY_LOGIC` engine in [js/state.js](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/js/state.js) to toggle features globally:
| Category | Expiry | Batch | Size/Color | IMEI/Serial | Warranty | Default Tax |
| :--- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---: |
| **Grocery** | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | 5% |
| **Fashion** | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | 15% |
| **Electronics** | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | 10% |
| **Cosmetics** | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | 8% |
| **Hardware** | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | 15% |

---

## 3. Module Breakdown

### 🛒 Point of Sale (POS)
- **File**: [js/pos.js](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/js/pos.js), [pos.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/pos.html)
- **Features**: 
    - Real-time cart management.
    - Multi-payment support (Cash, Mobile, Card, EMI).
    - Customer Loyalty points (Earn & Redeem).
    - Category-aware item selection (IMEI for Electronics, Size/Color for Fashion).
    - Hotkeys and barcode scanner support.

### 📦 Inventory & Products
- **Files**: [products.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/products.html), [categories.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/categories.html), [brands.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/brands.html), [stock.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/stock.html)
- **Features**:
    - SKU Generation and Barcode Printing.
    - Advanced Product Modal with dynamic fields based on Category.
    - Low-stock alerts and threshold management.
    - Stock Transfer between branches.

### 💰 Accounting & Finance
- **Files**: [accounting.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/accounting.html), [dues.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/dues.html), [cashflow.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/cashflow.html), [purchase.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/purchase.html)
- **Features**:
    - Account Balances: Cash-in-hand, Bank, bKash, Nagad.
    - Dues Tracking: Overdue alerts and partial collection.
    - Cashflow: Tracking deposits, withdrawals, and ownership transfers.
    - Expense management with breakdown analysis.

### 📊 Reports & Analytics
- **File**: [reports.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/reports.html), [dashboard.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/dashboard.html)
- **Features**:
    - Real-time P&L (Profit & Loss) Summary.
    - Visual Analysis: Sales vs. Profit trends (Chart.js), Expense breakdown.
    - Exporting: Excel and PDF stock/sales reports.

### 👥 HR & People
- **Files**: [employees.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/employees.html), [customers.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/customers.html), [suppliers.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/suppliers.html)
- **Features**:
    - Staff Payroll: Salary management, payment tracking, and dues.
    - Advanced Supplier Profiles: Opening balance, ledger tracking, and liability management.

---

## 4. SaaS Readiness & Security

### Multi-Tenancy (Simulated)
- The system is designed for multi-tenant SaaS. Currently, tenancy is handled via `isLoggedIn` and `shopName` in [js/state.js](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/js/state.js).
- **Branches**: Support for "Main Branch" and sub-branches with cross-branch stock transfers.

### User Roles & Permissions
Managed in [settings.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/settings.html) and [js/state.js](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/js/state.js):
- **Admin**: Full system access.
- **Manager**: Sales, Stock, and limited Reporting. No Accounting/Settings.
- **Salesman**: POS, Invoices, and Customer viewing only.

---

## 5. Technical Insights & Logic
- **Invoice Rendering**: [invoice.html](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/invoice.html) uses `sessionStorage` to pass data from POS to the print-ready invoice view.
- **Responsive Layout**: Sidebar collapses on mobile with a backdrop overlay, controlled via [AppLayout](file:///d:/nextWEB%20-%20developers%20file/inventory%20management%20software/js/layout.js#6-272) class.
- **Data Flow**: `UI.showToast` and `UI.confirm` provide consistent UX across the 16+ modules.

---

## 6. Identified Improvement Opportunities
1. **Backend Integration**: Move from `localStorage` to a robust API (Express/Django) for true multi-user sync and data security.
2. **Real-time Notifications**: Implement WebSockets for real-time stock alerts across branches.
3. **PWA Support**: Add a Service Worker to allow POS usage in offline/low-connectivity environments common in many retail settings.
